sequenceDiagram
    participant C as CLI
    participant B as BuildManager
    participant FS as FileSystem
    participant T as TemplateEngine

    C->>B: build()
    B->>FS: Scan assets/** for .mermaid
    loop For each Category
        B->>B: Group diagrams by path
        B->>FS: Write diagrams.json in category dir
    end
    B->>FS: Read index.html template
    B->>T: Process Project Metadata
    T->>FS: Write root index.html
    B->>FS: Copy standard CSS/JS to dist/
    C-->>C: Log "Build Complete"
